# Goals

---

## Wiki-G1 Wiki Search & Tag System
**Status:** proposed
**Module:** wiki
**Tags:** stack:fullstack, module:wiki
**Depends on:** Wiki-G1

- [ ] Users can search wiki pages by title and content keywords with instant results
- [ ] Wiki pages support tags for categorization and filtering
- [ ] Tag-based navigation provides quick access to related wiki content
- [ ] Search results highlight matching terms and show page context
- [ ] Tag management includes create, edit, delete, and merge operations

